# The world is full of wonder

## Goals

- Scalable & Performant
- Modular & Flexible & Composable
- Observable
- Loosely-coupled, Microservice like

## Roadmap

- Standard RL training
- Hierarchical
- Dynamic network
- Multi agent system
- Evolution strategy
- Convex optimization

